hani has acquired the iconic Villa Certosa in Sardinia, previously owned by former Italian Prime Minister Silvio Berlusconi. The transaction, valued at around €350 million, secures a stunning property that spans 120 hectares. Plans are underway to convert Villa Certosa into a luxurious resort, enriching the Sheikh's already impressive portfolio of high-end properties.]]></description><link><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/real-estate/qatari-royal-buys-real-estate-larger-than-vatican-city-for-375-million-in-italy-featuring-remote-controlled-erupting-volcano-five-swimming-pools-and-a-secret-cave-to-hide-from-drones/articleshow/132314476.cms]]></link><guid><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/real-estate/qatari-royal-buys-real-estate-larger-than-vatican-city-for-375-million-in-italy-featuring-remote-controlled-erupting-volcano-five-swimming-pools-and-a-secret-cave-to-hide-from-drones/articleshow/132314476.cms]]></guid><pubDate>2026-07-10T21:14:17+05:30</pubDate><enclosure type="image/jpeg" url="https://static.toiimg.com/photo/msid-132315554,imgsize-240370.cms"/></item><item><title><![CDATA[Quote of the day by Haruki Murakami: 'And once the storm is over, you won’t remember how you made it through']]></title><description>&lt;img border="0" hspace="10" align="left" style="margin-top:3px;margin-right:5px;" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/132315270.cms" /&gt;<![CDATA[]]></description><link><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/quote-of-the-day-by-haruki-murakami-and-once-the-storm-is-over-you-wont-remember-how-you-made-it-through/articleshow/132315270.cms]]></link><guid><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/quote-of-the-day-by-haruki-murakami-and-once-the-storm-is-over-you-wont-remember-how-you-made-it-through/articleshow/132315270.cms]]></guid><pubDate>2026-07-10T21:11:43+05:30</pubDate><dc:creator xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/">TOI World Desk</dc:creator><enclosure type="image/jpeg" url="https://static.toiimg.com/photo/msid-132315680,imgsize-101538.cms"/></item><item><title><![CDATA[Three held in Greece over deadly bomb attacks targeting ruling party politicians]]></title><description>&lt;img border="0" hspace="10" align="left" style="margin-top:3px;margin-right:5px;" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/132315128.cms" /&gt;<![CDATA[Greece's anti-terrorism forces have taken swift action, detaining three individuals believed to be behind a wave of firebomb assaults targeting members of the ruling New Democracy party. Among the attacks was a tragic explosion in Thessaloniki, which claimed the life of a parliamentary candidate's mother. These arrests not only demonstrate the government's resolve to seek justice but also underscore Greece's challenging history with political extremism.]]></description><link><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/three-held-in-greece-over-deadly-bomb-attacks-targeting-ruling-party-politicians/articleshow/132315128.cms]]></link><guid><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/three-held-in-greece-over-deadly-bomb-attacks-targeting-ruling-party-politicians/articleshow/132315128.cms]]></guid><pubDate>2026-07-10T20:50:34+05:30</pubDate><dc:creator xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/">TOI News Desk</dc:creator><enclosure type="image/jpeg" url="https://static.toiimg.com/photo/msid-132315196,imgsize-198094.cms"/></item><item><title><![CDATA[Elon Musk claims SpaceX will send thousands of people to the Moon and Mars within the next 10 years]]></title><description>&lt;img border="0" hspace="10" align="left" style="margin-top:3px;margin-right:5px;" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/132314652.cms" /&gt;<![CDATA[]]></description><link><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/science/elon-musk-claims-spacex-will-send-thousands-of-people-to-the-moon-and-mars-within-the-next-10-years/articleshow/132314652.cms]]></link><guid><![CDATA[https://timesofindi